<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Introduction to Trade Finance and Overview of Trade Finance Products/Services.&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Introduction to TBML, Terrorism Financing &amp; Weapons of Mass Destruction (WMD).&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Overview of International Laws, Regulations and Industry Guidance on TBML best practices.&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">TBML Typologies &amp; TBML key obligations for regulated firmTrade Customers/Transactions Risk Assessments.&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Trade Customers/Transactions Due Diligence checks (Letter of Credit, Documentary Credits, Guarantees &amp; Open Account Transactions).&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sanctions, Embargoes, Dual-Use Goods Reviews and TBML Red Flags identifications.&nbsp;</span></li>
